    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip rear differential. This vehicle has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS unit refresh and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback expected of the M-chassis. While the paint and interior show minor wear consistent with a well-maintained enthusiast car, the mechanical vitals are strong, with recent fluid analysis confirming the health of the rod bearings.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
